          "fullContent": "<p>This article examines the compatibility of AI-powered mass surveillance with Article 8 ECHR and the Fourth Amendment. Using case studies from China, the UK, and the US, we argue that predictive surveillance violates the right to private life unless strictly necessary and proportionate.</p>"
