          "iconClass": "fa-user",
          "fullContent": "<p>We analyze lawsuits challenging government use of facial recognition (e.g., Portier v. City of London). Our empirical study shows higher false positive rates for women and dark-skinned individuals. The article recommends a moratorium until accuracy improves.</p>"
