          "title": "Access to Justice in the Age of Legal AI Tools",
          "iconClass": "fa-balance-scale",
          "fullContent": "<p>This paper evaluates whether AI-powered legal chatbots improve access to justice for low-income individuals. We conducted a randomized controlled trial with 500 pro se litigants. Results show increased filing accuracy but also a digital divide based on literacy and tech access.</p>"
