          "title": "Human Rights Impact Assessments for High-Risk AI Systems",
          "iconClass": "fa-file-alt",
          "fullContent": "<p>We propose a mandatory human rights impact assessment (HRIA) framework for high-risk AI systems, drawing on the UN Guiding Principles on Business and Human Rights. The article includes a step-by-step HRIA template for AI developers and deployers.</p>"
