          "title": "AI and Democratic Governance: Risks and Safeguards",
          "iconClass": "fa-vote-yea",
          "fullContent": "<p>This article examines the use of AI in election administration (e.g., voter registration, redistricting). We identify risks of manipulation and bias, and propose safeguards including open-source algorithms, pre-election testing, and post-election audits.</p>"
