          "iconClass": "fa-tree",
          "fullContent": "<p>We analyze the National Environmental Policy Act (NEPA) review process for clean energy projects on federal lands. The article critiques recent CEQ guidance that expedites solar and wind projects, and discusses litigation risks from environmental groups.</p>"
