          "iconClass": "fa-plug",
          "fullContent": "<p>This article examines FERC's Order 2023 on transmission grid planning and cost allocation. We argue that current rules favor incumbent utilities and propose reforms to promote competition and renewable integration. Case studies of successful grid modernization in Europe are included.</p>"
