          "iconClass": "fa-file-contract",
          "fullContent": "<p>This guide explains the legal risks of making ransomware payments to sanctioned entities. We analyze OFAC's enforcement actions (e.g., against BitPay) and provide a step-by-step compliance checklist for victim organizations, including license application procedures and reporting obligations.</p>"
