          "iconClass": "fa-shield-alt",
          "fullContent": "<p>This article examines common coverage disputes in ransomware claims, including war exclusions, sub-limits, and the definition of 'computer fraud'. We review recent case law (e.g., Merck v. ACE) and provide negotiation tips for policyholders.</p>"
