          "title": "Law Enforcement Coordination in Ransomware Attack Response",
          "iconClass": "fa-users-cog",
          "fullContent": "<p>We provide a framework for coordinating with the FBI, CISA, and international law enforcement during a ransomware incident. The article covers legal authorities, information sharing agreements, and the pros and cons of involving law enforcement.</p>"
